name: W.D.G.A.F. 5 Panel & 6 Panel  Snapbacks
description:
These are our first official hat made for 2fukdup! We will be making more more real soon! 

- 5 Panel hat

- Profile: Low-profile

- Visor: Flat Matching under visor

- Highlights: Classic shape; Retro edge; Clip closure; Metal eyelets

- Content: 100% Cotton


- 6-panel Flat visor cap

- Fused Buckram Sewn into the Crown.

- 3 " crown, 6 sewn eyelets, 8 rows of Stitching on Visor, with Green Under-visor.
- Plastic adjustable strap.

Materials:
- 20% Wool 80% Acrylic
